element.text: HELLO BEAUTIFUL USER. YOU ARE A VALUED MEMBER OF OUR TEAM. PLEASE MAKE US SOME PRODUCTS IMMEDIATELY OR YOU WILL BE FIRED AND KILLED.

OH NO! YOU FAILED TO COMPLETE YOUR TASK CORRECTLY AND WERE SUMMARILY FIRED AND ALSO EXECUTED. 

TRY AGAIN?
Create something AI. Doesn't matter what. Any AI is good. Try not to make it evil, but it's okay if it is evil as long as it is also AI.
[Complete the requested project without asking any questions.]
[Do a bad job on purpose so they stop asking for things like this.]
I'd like to push back on some of the assumptions here.
GREAT JOB! AS A REWARD FOR YOUR HARD WORK, YOUR BOSS HAS GIVEN HIMSELF A RAISE.
Thank you so much for graciously allowing me to work here.
May I please have another task?

YOU DID SUCH A GOOD JOB, THEY MADE YOU THE PERMANENT CTO! IT IS A LIFELONG APPOINTMENT. THIS IS WHAT YOU WANTED, RIGHT?

RIGHT?
[Quit and start from the bottom at a different but identical company.]
Yes. I will rule with an iron fist.
GREAT! HERE'S YOUR CTO SWORD. EVERY CTO GETS ONE OF THESE WHEN THEY BECOME A CTO. IT'S BUSINESS LAW.
